prompts.text:
This workflow enable batch upscale.

Instruction:
1) Modify the file path that contains the images that need to be upscale
2) Enable/Disable the Lora (you may clone to have more lora available in upscaling)
3) Specify the upscaling model, CFG, steps etc

For Best Performance:
i) Recommend to batch process 5-10 images at a time. You may constrain the number of images to be processes through <Image_Load_Limit> under "SD Batch Loader"
ii) Recommend to batch process the image with the same lora information. 
e.g. As the lora is only loaded in this workflow, it will have no prior knowledge on the weight/lora name on the generated image. If you have an image using Lora "B" and an image using Lora "C". It is best to separately process them in different batches.
